document_data.name: Nyu Lake
document_data.mainbody: '''Nyu Lake''' was a lake in the [[Alpuk]] region of the [[Great Glacier]].
document_data.Description: Nyu Lake was a salt water lake with an average depth of between {{SIrange|5|20|ft|long=yes}}.
document_data.Geography: Nyu Lake was located in eastern Alpuk just north of the [[Novularond]].
document_data.Flora & Fauna: [[Ring moss]] grew around the lake. It was the only place other than the [[Lugsaas Chain]] where the moss grew.
